    "The proximity to the optimized parameter scenario, especially for large p, indicates the power of the suggested parameter setting strategies and shows a clear improvement over the earlier work.",
    "Our methods reduce the optimality gap by a factor of 8 for p = 3 as compared to Ref.[9].",
    "Figure 4:4Figure 4: Energy landscape of xy-QAOA applied to a random portfolio optimization problem with (a,b) original and (c) rescaled objective.",
